search_result:
Smith.ai is a business services and process outsourcing company that offers clients outsourcing solutions for customer service, scheduling, call center operations, and web chatting. They are a fully remote organization with a headquarters in Los Altos, California. Their contact email addresses are support@smith.ai for existing clients and sales@smith.ai for new clients, and their phone number is (650) 727-6484. They have a mix of services, including "vanilla SaaS" with consumption overages for voice and webchat engagement, plus SDRs as a Service for outbound customer nurture. They serve over 3,000 customers and aspire to hit 5-6,000 by the end of the year.

Their website is https://smith.ai/, and they have a physical address in Los Altos, California, but the exact address is not publicly available. They have a great company culture with positive feedback from employees, and they are proactive in providing support and feedback to their team members.
